    "layout": "Starts with a full-bleed, viewport-height hero section featuring a centered headline stack over a dark gradient background. The main content that follows is contained within a centered max-width layout (~1200px) on a white background. Sections alternate between centered headline blocks, 3-column feature card grids, and 2-column text-and-image blocks. The navigation header is sticky, starting transparent over the hero and transitioning to a solid white with a bottom border upon scrolling.",
    "imagery": "The visual language is product-centric and informational. It primarily uses clean product UI screenshots, often contained within abstract shapes or simplified browser chrome. There is no lifestyle photography. Icons are monochrome and line-style. A grid of grayscale customer logos provides social proof. The overall approach is to use visuals to explain functionality and build trust, not to create abstract mood.",
